{"tid":505772,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"啱先行返屋企 有個自稱係由杜拜黎旅遊嘅人問我借錢","createTime":"2017-12-21T13:32:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-23T09:00:55.000Z","uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"26ff3f24c98a949de5455a095ddd4e7738700937","tid":505772,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:32:25.000Z","msg":"話說我聽緊歌喺度扮型<br />\n之後條友無端端搭我膊頭<br />\n問我識唔識講英文 咁我就自以為是講咗幾句流利嘅英文俾佢聽<br />\n咁佢就梗係打蛇隨棍上啦<br />\n同我講話好多人都唔識講英文得我識講<br />\n屌你係香港地搵個識講英文嘅有幾難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後話咩自己喺度拜黎<br />\n唔見咗銀包<br />\n仲俾埋報警張紙我睇<br />\n我見到張紙嘅時候<br />\n我心諗 屌你張紙甩晒色 扮嘢都扮得好啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲話想問我借錢去買少少嘢食<br />\n仲話佢屋企人已經嚟緊香港幫佢<br />\n我心諗 屌你賣咗身上面嗰啲金鏈鑽石都買到成間7仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我就好好人嘅 諗住比少少錢打發佢算啦<br />\n當係破財擋災<br />\n之後頂你個肺 獅子開大口<br />\n夠膽死問我拎成＄500去買嘢食<br />\n屌你肚餓買個杯面唔得嘅<br />\n＄500你想買啲乜嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後佢仲唔死心<br />\n見到我銀包有張金牛<br />\n就係咁催我俾佢 話自己真係超級肚餓<br />\n聰明嘅我梗係死都唔俾佢啦<br />\n最後我比＄10打發佢走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cfa79ceb14f899970f9ad50a04020528531d66c","tid":505772,"uid":1139,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:33:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62143b387c2198d41fa00e0fa436c25db480c326","tid":505772,"uid":53947,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-21T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你聰明到比人呃10蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我打發佢走咋 煩到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc89c927a0d7bea944021ee368404180c220310d","tid":505772,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-23T09:00:55.000Z","msg":"好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}